                <para> Properties : Type 'vec' of size 1. </para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>
                    <emphasis role="bold">Sum along (0=all 1=lines 2=Columns)</emphasis>
                </para>
                <para> Indicates the used rule to sum. For more information see the description part.</para>
                <para> Properties : Type 'vec' of size 1.</para>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
